{"tid":718060,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"試下一晚唔瞓嘅實驗","createTime":"2018-06-26T13:27:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-27T00:57:44.000Z","uid":151717,"like":3,"dislike":74,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"7ea1ea3a8a345dff65c50004420d2a083bd0614b","tid":718060,"uid":151717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T13:27:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/26/211935_d9cb025f3d912914ff34e2e74c3eecfb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F26%2F211935_d9cb025f3d912914ff34e2e74c3eecfb.png&h=b9303a9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如圖所示<br />\n<br />\n我將會每一個鍾影下自己做緊咩同精神大概係咩情況<br />\n<br />\n有人可能話一晚唔瞓好小事，但係對於一個平時早睡早起加受咗打擊嘅人黎講可以係一個挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n同埋我想測試下究竟我嘅精神狀態係咁脆弱嘅情況下會唔會爆煲<br />\n<br />\n所以為咗呢個實驗，我嘅精神狀態唔知會變成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係急不及待想玩玩了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acf9429a5b1d67bedc3bb1ee50a0cf636a5e99a3","tid":718060,"uid":2676,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T13:27:52.000Z","msg":"晒氣喇,一日,ON99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24fcb643fa72fe2f4d56fdc97af4f87e3deacb3f","tid":718060,"uid":167777,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T13:27:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪香港人呀 一晚通宵有幾閒"},{"pid":"897ab58b1dbd8bf4b115ddcecc40b8895070c123","tid":718060,"uid":89509,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T13:28:30.000Z","msg":"Cls <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔瞓一晚都開post